MALACAÑANG RESIDENCE OF THE PRESIDENT OF THE PHILIPPINES MANILA

PROCLAMATION NO. 209-A

RESERVING FOR SCHOOL SITE PURPOSES OF THE CLARIN SCHOOL OF FISHERIES A CERTAIN PARCEL OF LAND OF THE PUBLIC DOMAIN SITUATED IN THE MUNICIPALITY OF CLARIN, PROVINCE OF BOHOL.

Upon recommendation of the Secretary of Agriculture and Natural Resources and pursuant to the authority vested in me by law, I, FERDINAND E. MARCOS, President of the Philippines, do hereby withdraw from sale or settlement and reserve for school site purposes under the administration of the Director of Vocational Education, subject to private rights, if any there be, and the condition that the occupants shall be reimbursed of the value of their improvements thereon, a certain parcel of land of the public domain situated in the Municipality of Clarin, province of Bohol, and more particularly described as follows:

Nr-193

(National Reservation)

Republic of the Philippines

(Clarin School of Fisheries)

A PARCEL OF LAND (as shown on plan Nr-193), situated in the Poblacion, Municipality of Clarin, Province of Bohol. Bounded on the SW., along line 1-2, by Road, on the NW., along line 2-3, by Bohol Strait (Proposed Expansion of Fisheries Site); on the NE., along lines 3-4-5, by Proposed Fisheries Fishpond Site; on the SE., along line 5-6, by property of Catalina Vda. de Sanchez, along line 6-7, by property of Victoriano Castillo, along line 7-8, by property of Sabiniano Cabradores, along line 8-9, by property of Catalina Vda. de Zafra, along line 9-10, by property of Simeon Patindol, along line 10-11, by property of Catalina Vda. de Zafra, along line 11-12, by property of Donata Vda. de Regodon, along line 12-13, by property of Felicisimo Umpad, along line 13-14, by property of Donata Vda. de Regodon, and along line 14-15, by property of Juana Vda. de Camacho; on the SW., and SE., along lines 15-16-17, by property of Lucio L. Canoto on the SW., and SE., along lines 17-18-1, by property of Ruperto Mascariñas. Beginning at a point marked “1” on plan, being N. 63 deg. 03′ E., 3007.75 m. B.L.L.M. 1, Mp. of Tubigon, Bohol;

